<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Leupold<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>lantgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> zum
                                <expan>Lewtemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr gnade aber
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> diener <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz
                        wir die auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>wissen</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu sein etlich
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> kawfflewt und der
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> die die sache antrift,
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> niht anheim, doch als wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> nehst <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> hoffen wir, ewr gnade
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>stee</expan> selbs wol, daz wir darczu niht
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> künnen, weil wir niht
                                <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, welh die
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> sint <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> wie die
                        heissen. Weͣr <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> kein der ewr, der maynet, daz er
                        in <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuss</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, wenn uns denn von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> wurde, so <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir darczu <expan>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Thome <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
